    "summary": "I'm a UX Designer living in Utrecht. What drives me is \n\nthe power of visual design.\nVisualization is a powerful method that uses the imagination of yourself and that of your target group. This enables them to attract and accomplish goals in their lifes and delivers you a great return on those business needs. \n\nThe language of the mind\nLanguage in itself is the most complex human behaviour. I'm always curious to what more there is than what people say, the thing we call spoken language, and how it's connected with that which drives our motivations.\n\nThe essence of teamwork\nGreat results require effective teamwork. It's because of that, that i enabled myself to understand how the language of front-end development works to bridge the gap between different disciplines en reduce failure in communication.",
